  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>No magical creature is more iconic in Iblydan lore than the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.aonprd.com/MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Medusa\">medusa</a>. Perhaps your lineage traces back to a medusa, or an ancestor survived a medusa’s petrifying gaze and was forever changed by the experience. However the medusa’s influence entered your bloodline, when you bloodrage, you gain fearsome and ancient powers.</em><br><br>Bonus Feats:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.Q1cY8r0Pvb66pMG0]{Alertness}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.pmAO1Sni8xx71pLF]{Blind-Fight}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.fVRnBIHR4Jq6btvm]{Great Fortitude}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.Uuiu3p982omhMEPj]{Improved Initiative}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.2aTFNMs3pW6nUBlr]{Improved Unarmed Strike}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.O0jbkTJcIji9BNiF]{Intimidating Prowess}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.8snLqsJN4LLL00Nq]{Toughness}</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Bonus Spells:&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.9tww9fc9049h6iqc]{Cause Fear} (7th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.tkjnm3lw7ni82tag]{Resist Energy} (10th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.78kwl5t99j9e8tzh]{Hold Person} (13th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.knyako6zopc1chrv]{Stoneskin} (16th)</li>\n</ul>",
